I am using "HubSpot/api-client" library in PHP. I am trying to implement API GET request by given email address to fetch a user Default and Custom properties from Contact object. I implement the following Code to implement the GET request ...
```public function getContact(string $email): ?SimplePublicObject
{
    $filter = new Filter();
    $filter
        -&gt;setOperator('EQ')
        -&gt;setPropertyName('email')
        -&gt;setValue($email);

    $filterGroup = new FilterGroup();
    $filterGroup-&gt;setFilters([$filter]);

    $searchRequest = new PublicObjectSearchRequest();
    $searchRequest-&gt;setFilterGroups([$filterGroup]);

    $contactsResults = $this-&gt;hubSpot
        -&gt;crm()
        -&gt;contacts()
        -&gt;searchApi()
        -&gt;doSearch($searchRequest)
        -&gt;getResults();
    //$this-&gt;hubSpot-&gt;crm()-&gt;contacts()-&gt;basicApi()-&gt;getPage($email);

    return $contactsResults[0] ?? null;
}```
But the following code is only return the Default properties.  Any help to retrieve Custom properties as well?
